2025-12-23T17:20:40.6803950+01:00 0HNI27ONKT16O:0000007F [INF] Executed DbCommand ("10"ms) [Parameters=[""], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']"
""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[AcademicDegree], [t].[FirstName], [t].[HireDate], [t].[ImageId], [t].[LastName], [t].[Status], [t].[UserId], [s1].[TeacherId], [s1].[SubjectId], [s1].[Id], [s1].[Credits], [s1].[Description], [s1].[Name], [s1].[TotalClasses], [s2].[TeacherId], [s2].[SchoolClassId], [s2].[Id], [s2].[ClassName], [s2].[CourseId], [s2].[EndDate], [s2].[StartDate]
FROM [Teachers] AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t0].[TeacherId], [t0].[SubjectId], [s].[Id], [s].[Credits], [s].[Description], [s].[Name], [s].[TotalClasses]
    FROM [TeacherSubjects] AS [t0]
    INNER JOIN [Subjects] AS [s] ON [t0].[SubjectId] = [s].[Id]
) AS [s1] ON [t].[Id] = [s1].[TeacherId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[TeacherId], [t1].[SchoolClassId], [s0].[Id], [s0].[ClassName], [s0].[CourseId], [s0].[EndDate], [s0].[StartDate]
    FROM [TeacherSchoolClasses] AS [t1]

FROM [SchoolClasses] AS [s]

    SELECT TOP(1) [t].[Id], [t].[AcademicDegree], [t].[FirstName], [t].[HireDate], [t].[ImageId], [t].[LastName], [t].[Status], [t].[UserId]

) AS [t2]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t0].[TeacherId], [t0].[SchoolClassId], [s].[Id], [s].[ClassName], [s].[CourseId], [s].[EndDate], [s].[StartDate], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CreatedAt], [c].[Description], [c].[Duration], [c].[IsActive], [c].[Name], [c].[UpdatedAt], [s0].[Id] AS [Id1], [s0].[EnrollmentDate], [s0].[FirstName], [s0].[ImageId], [s0].[LastName], [s0].[SchoolClassId] AS [SchoolClassId0], [s0].[Status], [s0].[UserId]
